700
00:48:08,865 --> 00:48:11,618
Don't share and claim every bit of credit!

701
00:48:31,555 --> 00:48:33,014
Why did you fire Writer Park?

702
00:48:33,098 --> 00:48:35,976
-Please knock before you come out.
-Why did you fire her?

703
00:48:36,059 --> 00:48:38,103
Have you ever seen a bastard share credit?

704
00:48:40,188 --> 00:48:41,523
I'm writing alone and taking full credit.

705
00:48:42,149 --> 00:48:44,443
All the glory and criticism
will be mine alone.

706
00:48:45,277 --> 00:48:47,946
No one will say it's good
if two people write it.

707
00:48:48,447 --> 00:48:49,281
Just wait.

708
00:48:50,699 --> 00:48:55,412
I'll show you how ruthless
and downright dirty I can be.

709
00:48:55,495 --> 00:48:56,455
I'll show you

710
00:48:56,538 --> 00:48:59,082
