711
00:49:24,691 --> 00:49:25,567
Damn it.

712
00:49:37,037 --> 00:49:39,998
CEO KO HYE-JIN

713
00:49:42,793 --> 00:49:44,127
I was wrong.

714
00:49:46,838 --> 00:49:48,381
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

715
00:49:54,262 --> 00:49:55,388
You did nothing wrong.

716
00:49:55,472 --> 00:49:56,848
I was wrong.

717
00:49:57,432 --> 00:49:58,767
You did nothing wrong.

718
00:49:59,392 --> 00:50:00,435
I was wrong.

719
00:50:06,149 --> 00:50:07,108
I'll just

720
00:50:08,443 --> 00:50:09,653
aim for third place.

721
