It attracts attention.

728
00:51:22,684 --> 00:51:24,102
But that's why you wear them.

729
00:51:24,185 --> 00:51:25,228
To attract attention.

730
00:51:26,146 --> 00:51:26,980
You know what?

731
00:51:27,522 --> 00:51:30,358
I've never seen Oh Jeong-hui
wear anything but heels,

732
00:51:31,318 --> 00:51:32,402
except when she's acting.

733
00:51:33,445 --> 00:51:36,907
She uses the clicking sounds
to intimidate people

734
00:51:36,990 --> 00:51:39,117
and changes the atmosphere in an instant,

735
00:51:40,160 --> 00:51:42,913
while exuding this energy
that she's going to win, no matter what.

736
00:51:44,915 --> 00:51:46,166
That's why no one can beat her.

737
00:51:47,584 --> 00:51:49,169
I respect that about her.

738
00:51:53,048 --> 00:51:56,051
When I get old,
even if I don't take care of my father,

739
00:51:56,134 --> 00:51:58,053
I'll take care of Oh Jeong-hui
to the very end.

740
00:52:01,973 --> 00:52:02,807
You know,

741
00:52:03,433 --> 00:52:05,894
