you care for your grandmother.

742
00:52:16,655 --> 00:52:18,573
What does it mean to be impressive?

743
00:52:19,574 --> 00:52:21,493
I know what it means to be cool.

744
00:52:22,452 --> 00:52:24,329
What makes a person impressive?

745
