What's wrong?

750
00:53:07,789 --> 00:53:08,832
What is it?

751
00:53:12,377 --> 00:53:13,753
I'm Byeon Si-on.

752
00:53:17,549 --> 00:53:19,384
I'm sorry I didn't tell you sooner.

753
00:54:11,978 --> 00:54:12,854
<i>It's a good thing</i>

754
00:54:13,855 --> 00:54:15,982
<i>I didn't raise you.</i>

755
00:54:18,651 --> 00:54:19,736
<i>You turned out well.</i>

756
00:54:38,922 --> 00:54:39,839
