and do yours first.

764
00:55:29,347 --> 00:55:30,390
Thank you!

765
00:55:30,473 --> 00:55:31,391
Thank you!

766
00:55:32,183 --> 00:55:33,351
Focus.

767
00:55:34,102 --> 00:55:36,312
And be ready, Hwang Dong-man.

768
00:55:36,396 --> 00:55:37,939
Yes, sir! Hwang Dong-man reporting!

769
00:55:38,022 --> 00:55:40,066
I'll focus and be ready, sir!

770
00:55:40,150 --> 00:55:40,984
Will do, sir!

771
00:55:49,117 --> 00:55:50,410
My film's going into production.

772
00:55:55,123 --> 00:55:56,332
Noh Kang-sik will be in it.

773
00:56:00,670 --> 00:56:01,796
I think spring is coming.

774
00:56:17,979 --> 00:56:20,607
HYOWON MANSION

775
00:56:36,748 --> 00:56:38,124
I'm going to be busy now.

776
00:56:39,667 --> 00:56:41,211
I might not make it home often.

777
00:56:42,754 --> 00:56:43,963
But I'll call every day.

778
00:56:48,593 --> 00:56:50,178
What's your purpose in life?

779
00:56:53,181 --> 00:56:55,016
What's your purpose in life?

780
00:56:57,518 --> 00:56:58,394
Humor.

781
00:57:01,898 --> 00:57:03,024
I'm just going to live life

782
00:57:04,359 --> 00:57:05,777
with a sense of humor.

783
00:57:11,074 --> 00:57:11,908
You passed.

784
00:57:26,005 --> 00:57:27,590
